\c 9
\s Vanhu, vakazogara Jerusarema, shure kokutapwa kwavo
\p
\v 1 Zvino Israeri wese wakaverengwa nemadzinza \add ake\add*; tarirai, akanyorwa mubhuku remadzimambo aIsraeri; asi VaJudha vakatapirwa kuBhabhironi nekuda kwekudarika kwavo.
\p
\v 2 Zvino vagari vekutanga vaiva panyika yavo nepamaguta avo vaiva vekwaIsraeri, vapristi, VaRevhi, neVaNetinimi.
\v 3 NepaJerusarema paigara vana vaJudha, nevana vaBhenjamini, nevana vaEfuremu, naManase;
\v 4 Utai mwanakomana waAmihudhi, mwanakomana waOmiri, mwanakomana waImiri, mwanakomana waBhani, wevana VaPerezi mwanakomana waJudha.
\v 5 Neve kuVaShiro: Asaya dangwe, nevanakomana vake.
\v 6 Nekuvanakomana vaZera: Jeueri, nehama dzavo, mazana matanhatu nemakumi mapfumbamwe.
\v 7 Nevanakomana vaBhenjamini: Saru, mwanakomana waMeshurami, mwanakomana waHodhavhiya, mwanakomana waHasenuwa.
\v 8 Nalbhineya mwanakomana waJehorami, naEra mwanakomana waUzi, mwanakomana waMikiri, naMeshurami mwanakomana waShefatiya, mwanakomana waReueri, mwanakomana waIbhiniya;
\v 9 nehama dzavo, zvichienderana nemazera avo; mazana mapfumbamwe nemakumi mashanu nematanhatu. Varume ava vese, misoro yemadzibaba zvichienderana neimba yemadzibaba avo.
\p
\v 10 Nekuvapristi: Jedhaya, naJehoyaribhi, naJakini;
\v 11 naAzariya mwanakomana waHirikiya, mwanakomana waMeshuramu, mwanakomana waZadhoki, mwanakomana waMerayoti, mwanakomana waAhitubhi, mutungamiriri muimba yaMwari,
\v 12 naAdhaya mwanakomana waJehoramu, mwanakomana waPashuri, mwanakomana waMarikiya, naMahasai, mwanakomana waAdhiyeri, mwanakomana waJahizera, mwanakomana waMeshuramu, mwanakomana waMeshiremiti, mwanakomana waImeri;
\v 13 nehama dzavo, misoro yeimba yemadzibaba avo, churu nemazana manomwe nemakumi matanhatu; vane simba kwazvo veumhare pabasa reshumiro yeimba yaMwari.
\p
\v 14 NekuVaRevhi: Shemaya mwanakomana waHashubhi, mwanakomana waAzirikamu, mwanakomana waHashabhiya, wevanakomana vaMerari;
\v 15 naBhakibhakari, Hereshi, naGarari, naMatania mwanakomma waMika, mwanakomana waZikiri, mwanakomana waAsafi;
\v 16 naObhadhiya mwanakomana waShemaya, mwanakomana waGarari, mwanakomana waJedhutuni, mwanakomana waAsa, mwanakomana waErikana, vaigara pamisha yevaNetofati.
\v 17 Nevachengeti vemasuwo: Sharumu, naAkubhi, naTarimoni, naAhimani, nehama dzavo; Sharumi waiva \add iye\add* musoro;
\v 18 uye kusvika panguva iyi, vaiva pasuwo ramambo kumabvazuva; ava vaiva vachengeti vemasuwo pamisasa yevana vaRevhi.
\v 19 Sharumu mwanakomana waKore, mwanakomana waEbhiyasafi, mwanakomana waKora, nehama dzake, veimba yababa vake, VaKora, pamusoro pebasa reshumiro, vachengeti vemasuwo etabhenekari; nemadzibaba avo, pamusoro pehondo yaJehovha, vachengeti vemukova.
\v 20 NaPinehasi mwanakomana waEriazari aiva mutungamiriri wavo pakutanga, Jehovha akava naye.
\v 21 Zekariya mwanakomana waMesheremiya, waiva muchengeti wesuwo pamukova wetende rekusangana.
\v 22 Zvino ava vakasarudzwa vakava vachengeti vemasuwo pamikova, mazana maviri negumi nevaviri. Ava vakaverengwa nemadzinza avo pamisha yavo, avo Dhavhidhi naSamueri muoni vavakagadza pamabasa avakatarirwa.
\v 23 Naizvozvo ivo ne nevana vavo vaichengetedza masuwo eimba yaJehovha, imba yetabhenekari, ne\add nguva dze\add*kurinda.
\v 24 Vachengeti vemasuwo vaivapo pamhepo ina, kumabvazuva, kumavirira, kumaodzanyemba, nekuchamhembe.
\v 25 Nehama dzavo pamisha yavo vaifanira kuuya mazuva manomwe nguva nenguva pamwe navo.
\v 26 Nokuti VaRevhi ava, vachengeti vemasuwo vakuru vana, vaiva pabasa ravakatarirwa, vaiva vakatarira makamuri nezvivigiro zvefuma zveimba yaMwari.
\p
\v 27 Zvino vaigara usiku vakapoteredza imba yaMwari, nokuti ngava raiva pamusoro pavo, uye vaiva vatariri vekuvhurwa k\add wayo\add* mangwanani ese.
\v 28 Zvino \add vamwe\add* vavo vaitarira midziyo yeshumiro, nokuti neuwandu vaivapinza uye neuwandu vaivabudisa.
\v 29 \add Vamwe\add* vavowo vaiva vakagadzwa pamusoro pemidziyo, nepamusoro pamidziyo yese ye\add nzvimbo\add* tsvene, nepamusoro peupfu hwakatsetseka, newaini, nemafuta, nezvipfungaidzo zvinonhuhwira, nezvibikiso zvinonhuhwira.
\v 30 \add Vamwe\add*zve vevanakomana vevapristi vavaisanganisa musanganiswa wezvibikiso zvinonhuhwira.
\v 31 NaMatitiya kuVaRevhi, mwanakomana waiva dangwe raSharumu, mu waiva akatarira basa rezvibhekewa mumakango.
\v 32 Nepahama dzavo, vevana VaKora, vaitarira pamusoro pezvingwa zvekuratidza, ku\add zvi\add*gadzira sabata nesabata.
\v 33 Uye ava vaimbi, misoro yeimba yemadzibaba eVaRevhi, mumakamuri vakasununguka; nokuti masikati neusiku zvaiva pamusoro pavo kuva pabasa.
\v 34 Ava misoro yemadzibaba eVaRevhi, misoro mumazera avo ese. Ava vakagara paJerusarema.
\p
\v 35 Zvino paGibhiyoni paigara baba vaGibhiyoni, Jeyieri; zita remukadzi wake raiva Mahaka.
\v 36 Nemwanakomana wake dangwe Abhidhoni, naZuri, naKishi, naBhaari, naNeri, naNadhabhi;
\v 37 naGedhori, naAhiyo, naZekariya, naMikiroti.
\v 38 Mikiroti ndokubereka Shimeami. Ivo vakagarawo pamwe nehama dzavo paJerusarema, pakatarisana nehama dzavo.
\v 39 Neri ndokubereka Kishi, Kishi ndokubereka Sauro, Sauro akabereka Jonatani, naMariki-Shua, naAbhinadhabhu, naEshi-Bhaari.
\v 40 Zvino mwanakomana waJonatani waiva Meribhi-Bhaari. Meribhibhaari ndokubereka Mika.
\v 41 Nevanakomana vaMika: Pitoni, naMereki, naTareya.
\v 42 Ahazi ndokubereka Jara, Jara ndokubereka Arimeti naAzimavheti, naZimiri; Zimiri ndokubereka Moza;
\v 43 Moza ndokubereka Bhineya, naRefaya mwanakomana wake, Ereyasa mwanakomana wake, Azeri mwanakomana wake;
\v 44 Azeri waiva nevanakomana vatanhatu; uye awa mazita avo: Azirikamu, naBhokeru, naIshimaeri, naSheariya, naObhadhiya, naHanani. Ava vanakomana vaAzeri.
